      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a id=\"upload\"&gt;</ph><ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>Create a new asset and upload a video file with REST API"
    },
    {
      "content": "In Media Services, you upload your digital files into an asset.",
      "pos": [
        13883,
