      "pos": [
        33604,
        33739
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "encode or transcode your mezzanine (source) file into a set of adaptive bitrate MP4 files or adaptive bitrate Smooth Streaming files (the encoding steps are demonstrated later in this tutorial),",
      "pos": [
        33742,
        33936
      ]
